Good! We're in luck! It seems there are no strong
monsters around.\n< Cecilia >

Let's go, Serena! We'll ignore the small fry and
dash through!\n< Cecilia >
Tch! Damn! A big one has shown up...!\n< Cecilia >
I'll take care of this one!\n< Cecilia >

Forgive me, Lady Cecilia! But don't do anything
reckless. It would be troublesome if there were no
one to give the reward!\n< Serena >
You've learned to talk the talk, huh.\n< Cecilia >
